075 per year.

 Since the sample size in the Phase 2 study is small and may overstate the effect of ANP therapy in general use, a hazard of 0.

167 per year was utilized in determining the sample size for the proposed Phase 3 protocol study, giving a hazard ratio (TMZ:ANP) of 2.

