 The primary efficacy hypothesis of the proposed protocol study is that ANP therapy provides for a significantly better PFS than does TMZ.

 This protocol study is event-driven (PD or death from any cause), and will be completed after 90 events have occurred.

 The required sample size in each treatment group is 79.

