05 per year is assumed.

 This study utilizes an intention-to-treat (ITT) analysis.

 It is event-driven (PD or death from any cause), and will be completed after 90 events have occurred.

 All subjects are evaluable for PFS from the time of randomization to the time of PD or death, regardless of therapy group, eligibility, or adequacy of follow-up.

 All study subjects who receive at least one dose of ANP therapy or TMZ are evaluable for safety.

